trans-unit.source: Represents progress data reported in an asynchronous operation.
trans-unit.target: Representerer pågår data som er rapportert i en asynkron operasjon.

trans-unit.source: This class contains properties that describe progress for the <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.CheckForUpdateProgressChanged>, <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.DownloadFileGroupProgressChanged>, and <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.UpdateProgressChanged> events.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen inneholder egenskaper som beskriver fremdrift for den <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.CheckForUpdateProgressChanged>, <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.DownloadFileGroupProgressChanged>, og <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.UpdateProgressChanged>hendelser.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.UpdateProgressChanged> </xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.DownloadFileGroupProgressChanged> </xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.CheckForUpdateProgressChanged>

trans-unit.source: Not every property in this class applies to each event.
trans-unit.target: Ikke alle egenskapene i denne klassen gjelder for hver hendelse.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Deployment.Application.DeploymentProgressChangedEventArgs.BytesCompleted%2A> and <xref:System.Deployment.Application.DeploymentProgressChangedEventArgs.BytesTotal%2A> represent the total number of bytes downloaded to date and the total number of bytes in the download operation, respectively; they apply to all three events.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Deployment.Application.DeploymentProgressChangedEventArgs.BytesCompleted%2A>og <xref:System.Deployment.Application.DeploymentProgressChangedEventArgs.BytesTotal%2A>representerer Totalt antall byte ned til datoen og totalt antall byte i nedlastingen, henholdsvis; de gjelder for alle tre hendelser.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.DeploymentProgressChangedEventArgs.BytesTotal%2A></xref:System.Deployment.Application.DeploymentProgressChangedEventArgs.BytesCompleted%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Deployment.Application.DeploymentProgressChangedEventArgs.Group%2A> names the file group corresponding to the current <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.DownloadFileGroupProgressChanged> event, and <xref:System.Deployment.Application.DeploymentProgressChangedEventArgs.State%2A> reflects the current stage of the download operation.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Deployment.Application.DeploymentProgressChangedEventArgs.Group%2A>navngir filgruppen som svarer til gjeldende <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.DownloadFileGroupProgressChanged>hendelse, og <xref:System.Deployment.Application.DeploymentProgressChangedEventArgs.State%2A>gjenspeiler gjeldende trinn i nedlastingen.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.DeploymentProgressChangedEventArgs.State%2A> </xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.DownloadFileGroupProgressChanged></xref:System.Deployment.Application.DeploymentProgressChangedEventArgs.Group%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of bytes already downloaded by this operation.
trans-unit.target: Henter antall byte som allerede har lastet ned i denne operasjonen.

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.CheckForUpdateProgressChanged>, the BytesCompleted property refers to the downloading of the deployment manifest.
trans-unit.target: For <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.CheckForUpdateProgressChanged>, egenskapen BytesCompleted refererer til nedlasting av distribusjon manifestet.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.CheckForUpdateProgressChanged>

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.UpdateProgressChanged>, the property refers to the download progress of the entire update, included the manifests, assemblies, and data files.
trans-unit.target: For <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.UpdateProgressChanged>, egenskapen refererer til fremdrift for nedlasting av hele oppdateringen, inkludert filer programmanifest, samlinger og data.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.UpdateProgressChanged>

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.DownloadFileGroupProgressChanged>, the property refers to the download progress of the entire set of files that are part of the named group.
trans-unit.target: For <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.DownloadFileGroupProgressChanged>, egenskapen refererer til fremdrift for nedlasting av hele settet med filer som er en del av gruppen navngitt.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.DownloadFileGroupProgressChanged>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Int64> representing the data already transferred, in bytes.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Int64>som representerer dataene allerede overført, i byte.</xref:System.Int64>

trans-unit.source: Gets the total number of bytes in the download operation.
trans-unit.target: Henter Totalt antall byte i nedlastingen.

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.CheckForUpdateProgressChanged>, the BytesTotal property refers to the downloading of the deployment manifest.
trans-unit.target: For <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.CheckForUpdateProgressChanged>, egenskapen BytesTotal refererer til nedlasting av distribusjon manifestet.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.CheckForUpdateProgressChanged>

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.UpdateProgressChanged>, the property refers to the download progress of the entire update, included the manifests, assemblies, and data files.
trans-unit.target: For <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.UpdateProgressChanged>, egenskapen refererer til fremdrift for nedlasting av hele oppdateringen, inkludert filer programmanifest, samlinger og data.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.UpdateProgressChanged>

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.DownloadFileGroupProgressChanged>, the property refers to the download progress of the entire set of files that are part of the named group.
trans-unit.target: For <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.DownloadFileGroupProgressChanged>, egenskapen refererer til fremdrift for nedlasting av hele settet med filer som er en del av gruppen navngitt.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.DownloadFileGroupProgressChanged>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Int64> representing the total size of the download, in bytes.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Int64>som representerer den totale størrelsen på nedlastingen, i byte.</xref:System.Int64>

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the file group being downloaded.
trans-unit.target: Henter navnet på filgruppen lastes ned.

trans-unit.source: You can initiate multiple calls to <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.DownloadFileGroupAsync%2A> and download multiple file groups simultaneously.
trans-unit.target: Du kan starte flere kall til <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.DownloadFileGroupAsync%2A>og Last ned flere filgrupper samtidig.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.DownloadFileGroupAsync%2A>

trans-unit.source: Use Group to determine which event callbacks correspond to which group.
trans-unit.target: Bruk gruppen for å finne ut hvilke hendelsen tilbakeringinger samsvarer med hvilken gruppe.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> containing the name of the file group, if the event occurred as the result of a call to <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.DownloadFileGroupAsync*>; otherwise, a zero-length string.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder navnet på filgruppen Hvis hendelsen oppstod som et resultat av et kall til <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.DownloadFileGroupAsync*>; Hvis ikke returneres en tom streng.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.DownloadFileGroupAsync*> </xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets the action that the process is currently executing.
trans-unit.target: Henter handlingen som utføres for øyeblikket prosessen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Deployment.Application.DeploymentProgressState"></xref> value, stating what element or elements the operation is currently downloading.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Deployment.Application.DeploymentProgressState"> </xref> verdi som angir hvilken elementet eller elementer operasjonen laster ned.
